WEBVTT

01:39.390 --> 01:43.310
[Road to Success]

01:44.800 --> 01:47.880
[Episode 15]

01:48.350 --> 01:51.070
That brat still isn't back.

01:51.590 --> 01:54.120
I really don't know
where else to look for him.

01:54.759 --> 01:55.479
He's back.

01:56.310 --> 01:57.560
You still know to come back?

01:57.560 --> 01:59.289
You could've made a phone call!

02:01.400 --> 02:02.680
I'm talking to you!

02:03.680 --> 02:04.400
Hello.

02:05.200 --> 02:06.600
I'm Ms. Lin, his teacher.

02:06.790 --> 02:07.560
I'm Coach Wang.

02:07.560 --> 02:09.430
Ms. Lin, Coach Wang.

02:09.430 --> 02:11.280
Come, here. Please sit.

02:17.590 --> 02:18.400
Ms. Lin,

02:19.079 --> 02:20.310
sorry to trouble you.

02:20.800 --> 02:23.030
This kid has always been a handful.

02:27.560 --> 02:28.890
What's with your hands?

02:29.000 --> 02:29.840
As you wished,

02:30.190 --> 02:31.310
I went to lay bricks.

02:31.310 --> 02:32.079
What?

02:33.590 --> 02:34.910
Why in the world would you

02:34.910 --> 02:35.960
go lay bricks?

02:35.960 --> 02:36.960
Are you insane?

02:37.079 --> 02:38.810
Yes, I'm insane.

02:38.829 --> 02:41.270
So what? What's wrong with laying bricks?

02:41.870 --> 02:43.400
Don't you think that's all I'm good for?

02:43.400 --> 02:44.560
I'm showing you!

02:44.710 --> 02:45.520
Listen, I won't

02:45.520 --> 02:46.960
spend another cent of your money.

02:46.960 --> 02:47.960
I can support myself.

02:47.960 --> 02:51.040
-You...
-Qin Ao, I'm hungry.

02:51.430 --> 02:53.400
Can you buy some snacks for me?

02:59.280 --> 03:00.190
This child...

03:02.510 --> 03:04.020
I'm sorry, Ms. Lin.

03:04.520 --> 03:05.920
Sorry you had to see that.

03:06.120 --> 03:07.120
The older he gets,

03:07.310 --> 03:08.910
the harder he is to raise.

03:09.430 --> 03:11.470
It's fine, Mr. Qin.

03:11.470 --> 03:14.590
Actually, we can see that
you love Qin Ao very much.

03:19.470 --> 03:22.250
What parents don't love their children?

03:23.030 --> 03:24.630
His mom passed away early,

03:24.840 --> 03:27.950
so I raised him all by myself.

03:28.150 --> 03:29.829
But he doesn't try his best.

03:30.079 --> 03:32.329
It's one thing to have bad grades,

03:32.590 --> 03:33.650
but he actually...

03:34.190 --> 03:35.930
He's actually even lying!

03:36.010 --> 03:37.630
I had no choice but to beat him.

03:37.630 --> 03:38.500
Sir,

03:38.800 --> 03:39.870
I believe

03:39.870 --> 03:41.000
Qin Ao didn't lie.

03:41.630 --> 03:42.740
Think about it.

03:42.910 --> 03:44.280
He has a bad temper,

03:44.800 --> 03:46.280
but he's very righteous.

03:46.910 --> 03:49.370
He always fights for what's right
at school.

03:50.470 --> 03:51.280
There's no way

03:51.750 --> 03:53.630
he's bullying his classmates.

03:54.870 --> 03:56.070
I also believe Qin Ao.

03:56.470 --> 03:57.810
Ms. Lin and I will

03:58.030 --> 04:00.160
investigate this matter thoroughly.

04:01.400 --> 04:03.060
What's there to investigate?

04:03.470 --> 04:04.930
Director Jin already said

04:05.530 --> 04:07.490
that no student was bullied.

04:07.750 --> 04:08.590
Mr. Qin,

04:08.590 --> 04:10.840
jumping to conclusions
without proper investigation

04:10.840 --> 04:12.510
isn't fair to him.

04:13.120 --> 04:14.850
Even if he didn't bully others,

04:15.190 --> 04:16.610
with his bad temper

04:16.950 --> 04:19.010
and how he talked back to the teacher,

04:19.040 --> 04:21.440
he'll get a severe penalty
and be punished.

04:22.070 --> 04:23.020
I only beat him to

04:23.160 --> 04:25.870
get him to swallow his pride and apologize

04:25.870 --> 04:27.530
so he doesn't ruin his future.

04:28.140 --> 04:29.540
It's all for his own good.

04:30.600 --> 04:32.600
Violence doesn't solve anything.

04:32.600 --> 04:33.480
No, no.

04:33.480 --> 04:34.330
Ms. Lin.

04:34.600 --> 04:36.330
Spare the rod, spoil the child.

04:36.390 --> 04:37.870
You beat a kid a couple of times,

04:37.870 --> 04:39.510
and he forgets it in a few days.

04:39.510 --> 04:40.370
It's fine.

04:40.600 --> 04:41.900
If I don't beat him

04:42.190 --> 04:43.159
and let him be,

04:43.159 --> 04:45.510
he'll eventually become a hoodlum.

04:46.360 --> 04:47.290
He won't forget.

04:52.390 --> 04:53.850
He'll always remember it.

04:55.310 --> 04:56.190
Mr. Qin,

04:57.310 --> 04:58.600
when I was 8 years old,

04:59.480 --> 05:01.010
my dad also wronged me once.

05:01.870 --> 05:03.310
His distrust back then

05:03.800 --> 05:04.600
haunted me

05:04.600 --> 05:06.390
for quite a bit.

05:07.390 --> 05:09.680
So much so that even after growing up,

05:10.480 --> 05:11.740
when I faced a setback,

05:12.510 --> 05:14.390
thinking of what my dad said then

05:15.600 --> 05:18.160
shattered my courage to face difficulties.

05:21.600 --> 05:22.720
You say Qin Ao is

05:23.950 --> 05:26.150
a rebellious kid.
Then when he ran away,

05:26.510 --> 05:27.920
why was the first thing he did

05:27.920 --> 05:28.980
to do manual labor,

05:29.560 --> 05:31.720
even though he said
he wouldn't depend on you

05:31.720 --> 05:32.720
and listen to you?

05:36.310 --> 05:37.270
Parents' words,

05:38.000 --> 05:38.430
sometimes,

05:38.430 --> 05:40.890
can really influence
a child's entire life.

05:48.120 --> 05:48.800
Mr. Qin,

05:49.430 --> 05:51.070
think about it.

05:51.750 --> 05:53.560
Is he really a bad kid?

06:02.800 --> 06:03.950
It's getting late.

06:04.190 --> 06:05.310
Mr. Qin,

06:05.310 --> 06:07.510
we won't bother you any longer.

06:09.680 --> 06:11.070
If possible,

06:11.630 --> 06:13.760
I hope you could tell him yourself that

06:14.430 --> 06:15.690
you love him very much.

06:25.360 --> 06:25.890
Let's go.

06:26.000 --> 06:27.060
Thank you, Mr. Qin.

06:27.800 --> 06:28.860
Take care, Ms. Lin.

06:40.800 --> 06:41.630
Are you OK?

06:43.270 --> 06:44.040
I'm fine.

06:45.000 --> 06:46.310
I hope Mr. Qin really

06:46.310 --> 06:48.370
understands where we're coming from

06:48.480 --> 06:50.210
and have a good talk with Qin Ao.

06:50.800 --> 06:52.950
Actually, you can tell

06:53.510 --> 06:56.390
that both father and son
care about each other.

06:58.070 --> 06:58.830
He will.

07:25.830 --> 07:27.040
Ms. Lin just left.

07:27.390 --> 07:28.510
She's quite nice.

07:32.270 --> 07:33.720
-Wait!
-What?

07:34.270 --> 07:36.000
You still want to scold me, huh?

08:16.950 --> 08:18.000
I'll do it myself.

08:29.240 --> 08:30.720
I'll go to the alley entrance

08:30.720 --> 08:33.179
to buy your favorite
fist-shaped meatballs

08:33.510 --> 08:34.450
and

08:34.669 --> 08:36.929
a bowl of wheat vermicelli

08:37.669 --> 08:38.870
to bring back for you.

09:38.360 --> 09:39.620
Hello, Director Qian.

09:40.240 --> 09:41.240
This is Lin.

09:43.270 --> 09:44.030
Yes,

09:44.550 --> 09:46.120
I took a sick day today.

09:49.790 --> 09:52.430
I'd like to ask you about Qin Ao.

10:26.790 --> 10:27.720
Feeling better?

10:28.240 --> 10:30.440
I'm fine. Can you do me a favor?

10:30.870 --> 10:31.480
Sure.

10:32.110 --> 10:33.240
That was quick.

10:33.240 --> 10:34.900
You didn't even ask what it is.

10:37.030 --> 10:38.360
I made you some hot tea.

10:39.720 --> 10:40.550
Thanks.

10:41.550 --> 10:43.770
So, how can I help?

10:44.670 --> 10:46.550
Do you have a tank top

10:46.550 --> 10:48.320
that shows your arms?

10:49.510 --> 10:50.320
What for?

10:51.910 --> 10:53.360
You'll know later.

10:56.360 --> 10:59.260
[White Tiger]

11:04.650 --> 11:06.160
[White Tiger]

11:31.320 --> 11:32.360
Are you shy?

11:37.670 --> 11:38.670
Tattoo stickers?

11:39.320 --> 11:40.960
Green Dragon on the left;
White Tiger on the right.

11:40.960 --> 11:42.160
Let me put them on you.

11:44.840 --> 11:46.550
What is it for?

11:48.520 --> 11:50.590
I just called Director Qian.

11:50.840 --> 11:51.720
He said

11:51.720 --> 11:54.450
Gu Yihao's parents
should be vegetable vendors.

11:54.720 --> 11:56.960
His father has a birth defect.

11:57.510 --> 11:59.790
So those bullies

11:59.790 --> 12:01.910
gave Gu Yihao nasty nicknames.

12:08.150 --> 12:09.480
What I'm sure of is

12:09.480 --> 12:12.270
that Wu Yunqi from Class 4 bullied him,

12:12.510 --> 12:13.720
but he didn't dare tell the teachers,

12:13.720 --> 12:15.000
fearing retaliation.

12:16.870 --> 12:18.870
He must've been bullied many times.

12:20.870 --> 12:22.480
With his background,

12:22.480 --> 12:24.740
he probably never had anyone back him up.

12:25.270 --> 12:26.510
So I think

12:27.270 --> 12:28.840
he didn't mean to lie.

12:41.030 --> 12:41.910
Done.

12:45.150 --> 12:48.510
So you want me to go
show Wu Yunqi and the others that

12:48.510 --> 12:50.510
Gu Yihao has someone backing him up?

12:53.600 --> 12:54.440
With these?

12:54.850 --> 12:56.550
Of course not.

12:56.550 --> 12:57.960
These were free gifts from an order.

12:57.960 --> 12:59.440
I just wanted to see how they look.

12:59.440 --> 13:01.240
I'll wipe them off for you later.

13:24.670 --> 13:25.730
Not bad.

13:26.270 --> 13:27.780
Before going to the office,

13:27.780 --> 13:30.040
you knew to swap out
the books in your bag.

13:30.790 --> 13:31.630
Relax.

13:32.240 --> 13:33.510
We came this time

13:33.510 --> 13:35.340
just to have a chat with you.

13:35.630 --> 13:37.560
You were quite sensible this time.

13:38.600 --> 13:39.240
Di.

13:40.080 --> 13:40.870
Give it to him.

13:40.870 --> 13:42.510
Good boys get candy.

13:42.870 --> 13:44.910
Just bought it. It's super sweet.

13:45.910 --> 13:47.510
Eat. Open your mouth.

13:47.790 --> 13:49.440
Don't do things the hard way.

13:49.440 --> 13:50.240
Eat it.

13:50.510 --> 13:53.790
Hurry up. Eat!

13:58.080 --> 13:58.870
Yihao.

14:01.240 --> 14:02.440
Who are you?

14:02.720 --> 14:05.520
I'm your cousin
who just came back from Yongchuan.

14:08.380 --> 14:09.540
Tell them loudly.

14:17.480 --> 14:17.960
Yes!

14:18.440 --> 14:19.710
He's my cousin,

14:19.960 --> 14:21.800
who just came back from Yongchuan.

14:21.800 --> 14:22.320
Nice!

14:23.860 --> 14:25.120
We're off. I'm sorry.

14:28.120 --> 14:28.910
Thank you!

14:31.480 --> 14:33.440
You're Qin Ao's coach, right?

14:34.320 --> 14:36.440
But I'm also your cousin.

14:37.320 --> 14:39.080
If you run into something like this again,

14:39.080 --> 14:40.540
come to me and the teachers

14:40.870 --> 14:41.750
anytime.

14:42.320 --> 14:42.910
OK.

14:45.030 --> 14:45.790
All settled?

14:47.630 --> 14:50.160
You're Ms. Lin,
the equipment keeper, right?

14:51.080 --> 14:54.030
You must be here for Qin Ao.

14:55.270 --> 14:56.080
I'm sorry!

14:59.270 --> 15:00.630
We're here for you.

15:01.550 --> 15:03.270
I'll tell the school that Wu Yunqi

15:03.270 --> 15:04.530
has been bullying you.

15:04.790 --> 15:06.520
The school will deal with it.

15:06.790 --> 15:08.890
Rest assured, we'll back you up.

15:11.270 --> 15:12.200
Don't you want me

15:12.510 --> 15:14.370
to clear Qin Ao and Lin Lu's names?

15:16.200 --> 15:17.460
This is your business.

15:17.630 --> 15:19.160
It's your decision to make.

15:22.270 --> 15:23.440
Thank you, Ms. Lin.

15:32.030 --> 15:33.430
You were so cool just now.

15:34.840 --> 15:36.370
Thanks for the compliment.

15:38.570 --> 15:41.740
[Zhiyuan Academic Building]

15:44.290 --> 15:47.630
[Sports Equipment Room]

15:48.750 --> 15:49.670
Hello, Ms. Lin.

15:55.870 --> 15:56.790
Come in.

15:57.910 --> 15:58.750
Principal.

16:04.750 --> 16:05.600
Ms. Lin,

16:06.440 --> 16:07.500
what's the matter?

16:07.910 --> 16:09.670
Gu Yihao has

16:09.670 --> 16:12.030
something to explain to you.

16:13.030 --> 16:13.840
Principal.

16:15.510 --> 16:18.270
Actually, Wu Yunqi and the others
from Class 4, Grade 12,

16:18.270 --> 16:19.530
have been bullying me.

16:22.480 --> 16:24.600
Go on. Say everything you want to say.

16:26.970 --> 16:28.020
My...

16:28.510 --> 16:31.200
My parents are vegetable vendors.

16:32.520 --> 16:34.670
My dad has a birth defect,

16:35.440 --> 16:37.040
so they always make fun of me.

16:38.600 --> 16:40.240
They pick places in school
without cameras

16:40.240 --> 16:41.030
to bully me.

16:42.630 --> 16:44.030
Wu Yunqi has good grades,

16:44.910 --> 16:46.390
so nobody would help me.

16:47.280 --> 16:48.950
Only Qin Ao and Lin Lu were

16:49.000 --> 16:50.060
willing to help me.

16:55.510 --> 16:56.310
Principal...

16:58.440 --> 16:59.700
I lied that day because

17:00.510 --> 17:02.770
I was so afraid of
Wu Yunqi and the others.

17:03.510 --> 17:06.400
But I've made up my mind
not to be afraid anymore.

17:06.400 --> 17:07.440
I want to be brave.

17:10.880 --> 17:12.510
Qin Ao, Lin Lu...

17:16.270 --> 17:17.270
I'm sorry!

17:26.500 --> 17:27.200
Principal,

17:28.440 --> 17:30.370
Qin Ao and Lin Lu did nothing wrong.

17:30.720 --> 17:31.920
They stopped Wu Yunqi and the others

17:31.920 --> 17:32.920
from bullying me.

17:34.000 --> 17:34.920
Please...

17:37.030 --> 17:38.510
clear Qin Ao's name.

17:39.720 --> 17:40.440
Principal,

17:41.550 --> 17:42.810
that's not important.

17:44.920 --> 17:46.780
If I encounter such a thing again,

17:47.400 --> 17:48.930
I'll still step in and help.

17:56.790 --> 17:58.590
I understand the situation now.

17:59.270 --> 18:00.200
I will handle it.

18:05.270 --> 18:05.940
You see?

18:06.160 --> 18:08.510
A hero's grievances
will always be redressed.

18:08.510 --> 18:13.160
-I'm the last hero of the Qin family!
-Here is an announcement.

18:13.370 --> 18:15.970
-The school would like to commend
-Awesome!

18:15.990 --> 18:18.000
Qin Ao and Lin Lu from Class 5, Grade 12,

18:18.000 --> 18:19.790
for their courageous act.

18:20.480 --> 18:21.830
We'd also like to reiterate

18:21.830 --> 18:23.200
that the school

18:23.200 --> 18:26.270
will not tolerate any form of bullying
among students.

18:26.270 --> 18:28.960
An anti-bullying committee
has been set up.

18:28.960 --> 18:30.830
If such incidents happen again,
please contact

18:29.350 --> 18:30.850
[Reap what you sow;
diligent or idle, only you know]

18:30.830 --> 18:33.000
-the teachers of the committee.
-That's too much!

18:33.000 --> 18:34.660
We'll crack down on bullying.

18:35.160 --> 18:36.400
The next song is

18:36.400 --> 18:38.880
dedicated to the two heroic students.

18:47.830 --> 18:50.970
[Knowledge is Boundless]

18:52.240 --> 18:53.400
Hey! Um,

18:53.400 --> 18:54.240
hear me out.

18:54.790 --> 18:57.530
The football team is now
the heroes of the school.

18:58.070 --> 18:59.680
So we're not bad students.

18:58.370 --> 19:01.260
♪ Who hasn't known
the dark of night and uncertainty? ♪

19:02.210 --> 19:05.680
♪ Stumbling, covered in wounds,
losing direction ♪

19:02.350 --> 19:05.550
-See you at the monthly exam!
-See you at the monthly exam!

19:06.210 --> 19:12.120
♪ Wandering alone,
gaining strength through pain ♪

19:14.490 --> 19:17.160
♪ Riding the wind,
chasing an unknown horizon ♪

19:18.350 --> 19:19.160
♪ Looking up ♪

19:19.070 --> 19:22.270
When that kid Qin Ao yelled,
"See you at the monthly exam,"

19:23.400 --> 19:24.940
so proud and spirited,

19:25.350 --> 19:28.150
he almost blew the roof
off the academic building.

19:29.960 --> 19:30.820
How wonderful.

19:31.960 --> 19:34.290
He and his dad
have also worked things out.

19:35.270 --> 19:37.270
Your words are very powerful.

19:42.750 --> 19:43.550
What's wrong?

19:43.720 --> 19:45.050
Still not feeling well?

19:45.880 --> 19:48.540
Maybe I've just been too tired.
I feel a bit cold.

19:53.350 --> 19:54.790
Looks like you have a slight fever.

19:54.790 --> 19:56.030
Let's head home.

20:11.270 --> 20:13.110
Where do you put your medicine?
I'll get it.

20:13.110 --> 20:14.310
In this drawer.

20:15.000 --> 20:16.830
Go rest on the sofa. I'll get it.

20:35.680 --> 20:37.140
This medicine is expired.

20:37.590 --> 20:38.850
I'll order a delivery.

20:42.550 --> 20:44.680
Let's put a cooling patch on you first.

20:57.110 --> 20:58.240
Rest up tomorrow.

20:58.590 --> 20:59.450
Take a sick day.

21:02.110 --> 21:02.850
By the way,

21:03.200 --> 21:05.330
I've registered for
a school pass for you.

21:05.330 --> 21:07.790
You still need to
fill in some personal info.

21:08.070 --> 21:09.240
I don't know yours.

21:10.270 --> 21:11.830
You might have to fill it in yourself.

21:11.830 --> 21:12.990
I'll do that later.

21:14.480 --> 21:15.710
Go rest in your room.

21:15.730 --> 21:17.530
I'll wait for the delivery here.

21:18.310 --> 21:19.310
Thank you.

21:52.640 --> 21:53.150
[Lenovo Browser]

21:56.610 --> 21:56.940
[Lenovo Browser]

21:57.420 --> 21:57.980
[Lenovo App Store]

21:59.100 --> 21:59.660
[WPS Office]

22:00.130 --> 22:00.820
[QQ]

22:02.530 --> 22:03.630
[QQ]

22:03.920 --> 22:05.500
[Psychology Books Discussion Group Chat]

22:05.570 --> 22:07.970
[Global Psychology Group Chat]

22:11.840 --> 22:13.830
[Global Psychology Group Chat]

22:14.050 --> 22:15.800
[Spade Q]

22:27.650 --> 22:27.940
[Spade Q]

22:28.110 --> 22:31.440
[Global Psychology Group Chat]

22:31.610 --> 22:37.220
[I hate you!]

22:37.250 --> 22:37.870
[I hate you!]

22:37.900 --> 22:38.500
[New Year has passed just like that]

22:38.530 --> 22:39.030
[How've you been today?]

22:39.060 --> 22:39.360
[Peaches are supreme]

22:39.390 --> 22:39.720
[Hehe, and you?]

22:39.740 --> 22:40.140
[You're a grape person?]

22:40.160 --> 22:40.470
[Grape! Sweet and sour!]

22:40.490 --> 22:41.080
[So? Which flavor candy
do you like the most?]

22:41.100 --> 22:41.500
[I'll enjoy them.]

22:41.520 --> 22:42.020
[Hope it eases your academic stress.
Don't let them go to waste.]

22:42.050 --> 22:42.950
[Here's a secret. These bear gummies]

22:42.980 --> 22:43.760
[are super hard to buy,
so I call them Lucky Candies.]

22:43.780 --> 22:44.610
[Ate one immediately. Not bad.]

22:44.630 --> 22:45.140
[Glad you got it. Feeling better?]

22:48.810 --> 22:49.890
[Jokes aside, I'll send you a gift later.]

22:49.920 --> 22:51.270
[Remember to accept it.]

22:51.290 --> 22:52.260
[Thank you. In the UK,]

22:52.280 --> 22:53.490
[you're the first friend
to send me a gift.]

22:52.790 --> 22:54.830
The two chat records are different.

22:53.520 --> 22:54.920
[I received your package!]

22:56.480 --> 22:57.440
Could there be

22:57.960 --> 22:59.730
two Spade Qs?

22:58.410 --> 22:59.780
[OK, looking forward to it.]

22:59.810 --> 23:00.680
[I've sent it out.]

23:00.700 --> 23:02.160
[You must try it right away.]

23:02.190 --> 23:04.450
[Jokes aside, I'll send you a gift later.
Remember to accept it.]

24:16.640 --> 24:17.200
Here.

24:17.920 --> 24:19.380
Take your medicine first.

24:53.640 --> 24:54.370
It wasn't me.

24:56.000 --> 24:57.400
I didn't do those things.

24:57.910 --> 24:59.060
I didn't do it.

24:59.750 --> 25:00.550
It wasn't me.

25:16.000 --> 25:16.830
I believe you.

25:20.160 --> 25:22.500
♪ Night slips through my fingers ♪

25:23.140 --> 25:27.390
♪ Embracing the coldness of wakefulness ♪

25:23.640 --> 25:24.680
Don't go.

25:27.980 --> 25:29.940
♪ Whispering my thoughts alone ♪

25:29.310 --> 25:30.270
Don't go.

25:30.460 --> 25:35.360
♪ Saying goodbye to the evening breeze
I chanced upon ♪

25:31.070 --> 25:32.240
Don't go.

25:34.030 --> 25:35.070
Don't go.

25:35.950 --> 25:38.750
♪ Staying with the jasmine blossoms
until late spring ♪

25:37.510 --> 25:38.350
Don't go.

25:39.270 --> 25:42.690
♪ Watching their elegance fade,
their fragrance disappear ♪

25:40.310 --> 25:43.590
Stay in Hongjing, OK?

25:43.660 --> 25:46.680
♪ I once dreamed of something beautiful ♪

25:47.340 --> 25:51.460
♪ And I accept that
regrets may grow wild ♪

25:49.440 --> 25:50.880
I haven't left yet.

25:52.140 --> 25:54.680
♪ Look, beneath the sunlight ♪

25:55.140 --> 25:59.380
♪ In the dancing specks of dust ♪

25:59.850 --> 26:02.760
♪ I'm grateful I never lost my sincerity ♪

26:03.270 --> 26:07.180
♪ Or my gift for happiness ♪

26:08.610 --> 26:10.650
♪ Sharing my warmth with a passing rain ♪

26:11.030 --> 26:12.270
Don't worry.

26:11.390 --> 26:15.140
♪ Quietly feeling its journey ♪

26:15.160 --> 26:16.090
I'm not leaving.

26:16.440 --> 26:18.860
♪ Like a firefly vanishing in an instant ♪

26:19.530 --> 26:23.240
♪ Still beautiful in its entirety ♪

26:24.100 --> 26:26.630
♪ There's no need to seek a final answer ♪

26:26.400 --> 26:27.550
What did you say?

26:28.440 --> 26:29.000
You saw that

26:29.000 --> 26:30.880
Lin Wanxing's QQ ID is Spade Q?

26:33.920 --> 26:34.920
See for yourself.

26:38.020 --> 26:41.910
[Spade Q]

26:44.710 --> 26:47.270
[Spade Q]

26:49.000 --> 26:50.000
All is solved.

26:50.880 --> 26:51.590
It's her.

26:52.400 --> 26:53.130
It's not her.

26:54.520 --> 26:55.410
At least,

26:55.440 --> 26:56.510
she's not

26:56.510 --> 26:58.180
the Spade Q who killed Jason.

26:58.350 --> 26:58.920
Wait,

26:58.920 --> 27:01.000
is Lin Wanxing's fever
making her delirious,

27:01.000 --> 27:02.590
or making you delirious?

27:02.590 --> 27:03.830
They're clearly the same person.

27:03.830 --> 27:05.360
What are you talking about?

27:15.410 --> 27:18.610
[Spa]

27:21.640 --> 27:23.080
What do you mean by that?

27:22.990 --> 27:24.350
[Spade Q]

27:27.350 --> 27:30.440
Simply put, I think
there are two Spade Qs.

27:31.480 --> 27:33.640
[Probability of Lin Wanxing
being Spade Q: 0%]

27:31.720 --> 27:34.920
The first Spade Q is patient and wise.

27:35.550 --> 27:36.350
Hello.

27:36.350 --> 27:38.480
Haven't heard from you in days.
Are you OK?

27:38.480 --> 27:40.110
Although she jokes around,

27:40.110 --> 27:41.790
she's absolutely a kind person.

27:41.790 --> 27:44.350
No, just busy with all my training.

27:44.350 --> 27:45.440
Don't exhaust yourself.

27:45.440 --> 27:47.510
Nothing's more important than your health.

27:47.510 --> 27:50.640
Friend, you sound
just like my mom right now.

27:53.510 --> 27:55.440
Biting the hand who feeds you, huh?

27:57.920 --> 27:59.200
Jokes aside,

27:59.200 --> 28:00.480
I'll send you a gift later.

28:00.480 --> 28:01.640
Remember to accept it.

28:01.640 --> 28:02.310
Thank you.

28:02.310 --> 28:03.240
In the UK,

28:03.260 --> 28:05.520
you're the first friend to send me a gift.

28:06.240 --> 28:07.070
You make this Spade Q

28:07.070 --> 28:09.130
sound like an angel sent from heaven.

28:12.480 --> 28:13.240
The second Spade Q

28:13.240 --> 28:14.500
is the exact opposite.

28:18.110 --> 28:19.370
I sent the package out.

28:19.790 --> 28:21.270
You must try it right away.

28:22.200 --> 28:23.880
OK, looking forward to it.

28:22.590 --> 28:26.070
[You must try it right away.]

28:23.880 --> 28:25.440
The second Spade Q

28:25.440 --> 28:26.880
is sinister and cunning,

28:26.100 --> 28:31.180
[I'll get mad if they go to waste.]

28:26.880 --> 28:29.000
skilled at luring and deception,

28:29.000 --> 28:30.130
ignoring all rules.

28:31.250 --> 28:32.000
By the way,

28:32.000 --> 28:33.590
about the gift,

28:33.590 --> 28:35.110
can you keep it a secret?

28:37.110 --> 28:39.240
Why? Afraid I'll show off?

28:41.240 --> 28:42.510
No.

28:42.750 --> 28:44.310
I just like to keep a low profile.

28:44.310 --> 28:45.640
Just between you and me.

28:47.790 --> 28:50.750
That's an interesting way to put it.

28:50.750 --> 28:51.590
I'll keep it a secret.

28:51.590 --> 28:54.350
The two Spade Qs have
drastically different images

28:54.350 --> 28:56.810
and totally different ways
of doing things.

28:57.920 --> 28:59.200
But that doesn't prove

28:59.200 --> 29:01.070
that they're not the same person.

29:01.680 --> 29:02.270
OK, sure.

29:02.270 --> 29:03.590
You've analyzed that

29:03.590 --> 29:04.640
Spade Q disguised themself

29:04.640 --> 29:05.900
to gain Jason's trust,

29:06.270 --> 29:09.130
so it's entirely possible
they're the same person.

29:09.270 --> 29:10.400
But right now, to me,

29:10.920 --> 29:12.250
they must be two people.

29:13.350 --> 29:14.610
I think you're biased.

29:14.790 --> 29:15.720
I have evidence.

29:17.480 --> 29:19.160
The chat records from Lin Wanxing's end,

29:19.160 --> 29:20.350
compared to what we got

29:20.350 --> 29:21.310
from Jason,

29:21.310 --> 29:22.240
are incomplete.

29:23.040 --> 29:24.320
Like, Lin Wanxing's records

29:24.120 --> 29:24.930
[Jokes aside, I'll send you a gift later.]

29:24.350 --> 29:26.340
only mentioned
she was giving Jason a gift,

29:24.960 --> 29:26.070
[Remember to accept it.]

29:26.430 --> 29:31.390
[Jokes aside, I'll send you a gift later.
Remember to accept it.]

29:26.830 --> 29:28.200
while Jason's records

29:28.750 --> 29:30.200
showed Spade Q encouraging Jason

29:30.200 --> 29:31.640
to taste it right away.

29:31.640 --> 29:32.920
But Lin Wanxing could have

29:32.920 --> 29:34.310
deleted some messages.

29:34.310 --> 29:35.480
Why didn't she just

29:35.480 --> 29:36.610
delete everything?

29:37.680 --> 29:39.160
So the more likely scenario is

29:39.160 --> 29:40.890
that Spade Q is just an account,

29:41.350 --> 29:43.680
and there are other users
besides Lin Wanxing.

29:43.680 --> 29:45.030
This person

29:45.030 --> 29:46.830
hacked into Lin Wanxing's account,

29:46.830 --> 29:47.720
chatted with Jason,

29:47.720 --> 29:49.350
and then deleted the messages.

29:49.350 --> 29:50.240
OK, OK.

29:50.240 --> 29:51.440
You've convinced me.

29:52.480 --> 29:53.880
What should we do next?

29:54.350 --> 29:55.030
We've at least

29:55.030 --> 29:56.790
eliminated a wrong option.
Now, we can only

29:56.790 --> 29:58.650
investigate from scratch again.

29:59.000 --> 30:01.200
Who would benefit from Jason's death?

30:01.720 --> 30:03.180
Who would want to harm him?

30:05.340 --> 30:06.060
This...

30:06.090 --> 30:07.710
This is a bit difficult.

30:08.310 --> 30:09.170
How about this?

30:09.550 --> 30:10.310
Look into whether

30:10.310 --> 30:12.550
there have been any similar cases
of star players

30:12.550 --> 30:14.480
being victimized in recent years.

30:16.230 --> 30:17.110
Understood.

30:23.490 --> 30:26.110
[Probability of Lin Wanxing
being Spade Q: 0%]

31:02.830 --> 31:04.690
Have the pumpkin millet porridge

31:04.960 --> 31:06.290
and take your medicine.

31:17.440 --> 31:18.830
Some think that
in the late Middle Ages,

31:18.830 --> 31:20.350
the highly important spice trade

31:20.350 --> 31:21.830
wasn't greatly affected.

31:22.270 --> 31:24.590
For the opening of
new shipping routes, everyone...

31:24.590 --> 31:25.350
Hello.

31:26.110 --> 31:27.310
Ms. Lin?

31:27.310 --> 31:30.060
-M-Ms. Lin.
-Ms. Lin.

31:30.240 --> 31:31.160
Ms. Lin,

31:31.160 --> 31:32.590
are you feeling better?

31:32.590 --> 31:33.440
Don't worry, guys.

31:33.440 --> 31:35.030
I'm good as new.

31:36.240 --> 31:37.280
Ms. Lin,

31:37.310 --> 31:39.240
Boss has changed so much.

31:39.550 --> 31:40.830
He's been so pumped up.

31:40.830 --> 31:42.030
Look at his textbook.

31:42.590 --> 31:43.880
He's been taking notes.

31:43.880 --> 31:45.590
And his notebook.

31:46.160 --> 31:48.830
-Copying ancient poems!
-"In the ninth year of Yonghe,

31:48.830 --> 31:50.350
the year of Guichou."

31:51.640 --> 31:54.240
Ms. Lin, exams are coming soon.

31:54.240 --> 31:56.240
-Am I up to it?
-Yeah.

31:57.130 --> 31:58.000
You'll be fine.

31:58.030 --> 31:59.000
Isn't it time

31:59.000 --> 32:01.400
for me to show you what I've got?

32:01.400 --> 32:02.510
Starting today,

32:02.510 --> 32:03.590
I'll predict exam questions for you.

32:03.590 --> 32:06.520
-Predict questions?
-Predict questions! Awesome.

32:06.600 --> 32:11.220
[7 days until the evil monthly exam]

32:06.750 --> 32:08.240
Today we're going to learn

32:08.240 --> 32:11.110
how to use words correctly.

32:11.110 --> 32:12.880
The first is "require."

32:14.030 --> 32:15.440
What does "require" mean?

32:15.440 --> 32:16.640
Qin Ao, you tell us.

32:20.590 --> 32:21.640
♪ A starlit night ♪

32:22.350 --> 32:23.510
OK, pay attention.

32:22.480 --> 32:26.930
♪ Secrets falling into my palm ♪

32:23.510 --> 32:25.510
"Require" means to make necessary.

32:27.770 --> 32:29.050
♪ Unraveling the mystery ♪

32:29.810 --> 32:33.840
♪ It was you who gave me this brilliance ♪

32:34.870 --> 32:36.050
♪ Lasting memories ♪

32:36.980 --> 32:41.460
♪ The distance
that brings our dreams closer ♪

32:42.080 --> 32:42.940
♪ To run toward you ♪

32:43.630 --> 32:48.210
♪ I keep practicing with no turning back ♪

32:45.200 --> 32:46.490
[7 days until the evil monthly exam]

32:46.500 --> 32:47.360
[6 days until the evil monthly exam]

32:47.380 --> 32:47.890
[5 days until the evil monthly exam]

32:47.920 --> 32:48.350
[4 days until the evil monthly exam]

32:48.380 --> 32:48.800
[3 days until the evil monthly exam]

32:48.890 --> 32:51.540
[2 days until the evil monthly exam]

32:51.570 --> 32:56.720
[1 day until the evil monthly exam]

32:51.680 --> 32:52.960
♪ There's nothing to fear ♪

32:54.150 --> 32:55.480
♪ Because you're with me ♪

32:58.630 --> 32:59.880
♪ The light shimmers ♪

33:01.330 --> 33:02.620
♪ Brilliant as stars ♪

33:04.240 --> 33:05.300
♪ Running towards you ♪

33:06.260 --> 33:07.450
♪ I keep moving fearlessly ♪

33:11.300 --> 33:12.280
♪ Walk side by side ♪

33:13.110 --> 33:15.230
♪ Become ourselves ♪

33:17.260 --> 33:18.200
♪ Amid the storm ♪

33:19.000 --> 33:23.440
♪ As our breaths slowly intertwine ♪

33:23.990 --> 33:25.110
♪ Heartbeats alternating ♪

33:26.150 --> 33:30.390
♪ A chemistry about to emerge ♪

33:31.340 --> 33:32.270
♪ The stars are shining ♪

33:33.060 --> 33:37.580
♪ Take my hand and run forward ♪

33:38.470 --> 33:39.320
♪ For you ♪

33:40.280 --> 33:44.820
♪ I'm willing to
keep practicing and practicing ♪

33:48.230 --> 33:49.790
♪ There's nothing to fear ♪

33:50.640 --> 33:52.170
♪ Because you're with me ♪

33:53.830 --> 33:54.920
Go, go. Here. Pass.

33:55.130 --> 33:56.590
♪ The light shimmers ♪

33:55.440 --> 33:56.000
You do it.

33:56.000 --> 33:57.440
Pass the ball. Hurry.

33:57.830 --> 33:59.110
♪ Brilliant as stars ♪

33:59.880 --> 34:01.830
-Go forward.
-Good one.

34:00.740 --> 34:01.800
♪ Running towards you ♪

34:02.480 --> 34:04.110
-Come on.
-Go. Here.

34:02.760 --> 34:03.820
♪ I keep moving fearlessly ♪

34:04.790 --> 34:05.680
Pass, pass.

34:07.800 --> 34:08.670
♪ Walk side by side ♪

34:10.920 --> 34:11.550
Come on.

34:13.630 --> 34:14.960
Next, group scrimmage.

34:17.760 --> 34:18.550
Um, Coach,

34:18.550 --> 34:20.360
can we t-take a 10-minute break?

34:20.510 --> 34:21.320
Yeah.

34:22.000 --> 34:22.600
What is it?

34:23.070 --> 34:24.960
Hello, my dear schoolmates.

34:24.960 --> 34:26.000
Today's campus

34:26.000 --> 34:27.070
-seems to be…
-Go ahead.

34:27.070 --> 34:28.710
Thank you, Ms. Lin!

34:28.710 --> 34:29.510
Thank you, Coach!

34:29.510 --> 34:31.840
I'm sure everyone's very nervous.

34:32.400 --> 34:35.840
That's right. The monthly exam results
will be announced today.

34:35.840 --> 34:37.230
The campus radio

34:37.230 --> 34:38.280
has prepared

34:38.280 --> 34:39.920
a light and cheerful song for everyone

34:39.920 --> 34:41.480
to relieve the tension.

34:41.480 --> 34:43.550
Please enjoy it quietly.

34:57.130 --> 34:57.670
Excuse me!

34:57.670 --> 34:59.190
Excuse me. Let me through.

34:59.190 --> 35:00.280
-Thanks. Sorry.
-Sorry.

35:00.280 --> 35:01.740
Excuse me. Let me through.

35:02.070 --> 35:03.230
Those in front, please don't block it.

35:03.230 --> 35:04.110
Excuse me.

35:04.110 --> 35:04.820
Where's mine?

35:04.820 --> 35:07.530
[Grade 12 monthly exam ranking]

35:24.030 --> 35:25.000
How did you do?

35:30.800 --> 35:31.670
It's OK.

35:32.000 --> 35:33.480
One exam doesn't mean anything.

35:33.480 --> 35:34.800
There's still a next time.

35:34.800 --> 35:36.070
Let's review everything

35:36.070 --> 35:37.550
and start over again.

35:37.780 --> 35:38.630
Can you hear me?

35:38.630 --> 35:39.630
Can you hear me?

35:39.630 --> 35:40.800
What are you doing—

35:41.440 --> 35:43.590
-This is the radio. I'm playing a song!
-Um, fantastic news!

35:43.590 --> 35:44.520
Fantastic news!

35:45.480 --> 35:46.410
Fantastic news!

35:46.520 --> 35:49.730
After winning the pennant,
Hongjing's football team

35:49.500 --> 35:53.010
[Campus Radio]

35:49.760 --> 35:51.160
has reached new heights!

35:51.550 --> 35:52.400
In this

35:52.400 --> 35:53.230
monthly exam,

35:53.250 --> 35:56.470
every football player
made it into the top 500!

36:03.150 --> 36:05.550
Oh, so you were messing with me!

36:09.000 --> 36:10.110
I, Qin Ao,

36:10.480 --> 36:12.680
ranked 478th

36:13.110 --> 36:15.710
in this monthly exam.

36:15.710 --> 36:18.190
I got 82 in Chinese,

36:18.190 --> 36:20.450
which is only 8 points away from passing.

36:20.550 --> 36:21.880
And for Classical Chinese,

36:21.880 --> 36:23.110
I improved by 1 point.

36:23.110 --> 36:23.920
Wait, the exams

36:23.240 --> 36:27.670
♪ Waiting for a dark cloud
to pass by you ♪

36:23.920 --> 36:25.880
are out of 150, aren't they?

36:26.760 --> 36:27.920
Enough!

36:27.670 --> 36:31.330
[Campus Radio]

36:28.710 --> 36:29.590
Are you done?

36:29.360 --> 36:33.940
♪ Listen closely to its cries ♪

36:30.850 --> 36:31.820
This is too much.

36:31.880 --> 36:33.280
Let me say one last thing.

36:35.730 --> 36:40.730
♪ The heavy rain will wash away
your reflection ♪

36:36.150 --> 36:38.550
Sports equipment keeper, Ms. Lin Wanxing.

36:41.620 --> 36:47.220
♪ And carry it toward distant scenery ♪

36:41.790 --> 36:42.990
Thank you.

36:47.350 --> 36:49.660
[Campus Radio]

36:48.480 --> 36:50.110
Thank you, Ms. Lin.

36:48.640 --> 36:54.300
♪ Every experience has its meaning ♪

36:50.840 --> 36:52.360
Thank you, Ms. Lin.

36:52.930 --> 36:54.730
Thank you, Ms. Lin.

36:54.760 --> 36:56.960
Thank you, Ms. Lin.

36:55.250 --> 37:00.020
♪ Scene by scene, they come together
to form who I am ♪

36:57.510 --> 36:59.440
Thank you, Ms. Lin!

37:00.150 --> 37:03.590
Thank you, Ms. Lin!

37:01.680 --> 37:07.060
♪ Even the wounds
that leave behind their marks ♪

37:07.980 --> 37:12.820
♪ Have taught me how to heal myself ♪

37:14.000 --> 37:19.660
♪ The love I have given,
the love I have received ♪

37:18.510 --> 37:19.710
[Qin Ao: 478th (up 122 places)]

37:19.760 --> 37:21.980
-I'm 478th!
-Really?

37:19.830 --> 37:23.140
[Grade 12 monthly exam ranking]

37:20.610 --> 37:26.090
♪ Every one of them gives me the strength
not to fear being hurt ♪

37:22.190 --> 37:25.400
-367th!
-I'm 478th!

37:26.880 --> 37:29.870
-I'm in the top 500!
-Top 500!

37:27.050 --> 37:32.660
♪ Let my tears be carried away,
back into the ocean ♪

37:32.280 --> 37:33.070
Ms. Lin.

37:33.520 --> 37:38.680
♪ And blown toward flowers
blooming far away ♪

37:34.190 --> 37:35.030
Without you,

37:35.760 --> 37:37.220
we could've never done it.

37:38.880 --> 37:39.960
Don't thank me.

37:40.070 --> 37:45.400
♪ I fill the blank spaces of life
with colors ♪

37:41.230 --> 37:42.890
You should thank yourselves.

37:43.960 --> 37:46.070
You're all wonderful students.

37:46.140 --> 37:51.880
♪ My dreams are not afraid to awaken;
they continue to exist ♪

37:47.440 --> 37:48.480
Actually,

37:49.920 --> 37:52.150
I'm the one who should really thank you.

37:52.660 --> 37:58.310
♪ I go beyond the dark clouds
and feel the haze disperse ♪

37:56.550 --> 37:57.880
I didn't bring tissues.

37:58.440 --> 38:00.230
Wanna borrow my clothes
to wipe your tears?

37:59.310 --> 38:05.010
♪ Let me understand myself more clearly ♪

38:05.110 --> 38:06.360
Are you trying to

38:06.360 --> 38:08.250
make me pay for your dry cleaning now?

38:08.250 --> 38:09.690
I can wipe them myself.

38:12.920 --> 38:14.550
Ms. Lin!

38:14.550 --> 38:15.800
Ms. Lin, we did it!

38:15.800 --> 38:17.360
-We did it!
-Ms. Lin!

38:17.880 --> 38:18.760
We did it!

38:23.230 --> 38:28.280
♪ Every experience has its meaning ♪

38:24.710 --> 38:25.880
Congratulations!

38:29.490 --> 38:34.020
♪ Scene by scene, they come together
to form who I am ♪

38:29.590 --> 38:31.530
Brothers, let's play... The scrimmage!

38:31.530 --> 38:33.650
-Let's go!
-Let's go!

38:35.920 --> 38:40.900
♪ Even the wounds
that leave behind their marks ♪

38:39.070 --> 38:40.400
Thank you, Ms. Lin.

38:42.080 --> 38:48.490
♪ Have taught me how to heal myself ♪

38:42.630 --> 38:44.190
What did he thank me for?

38:46.960 --> 38:48.420
It should be me and the kids

38:48.510 --> 38:49.630
thanking you.

38:51.100 --> 38:56.630
♪ The love I have given,
the love I have received ♪

38:57.670 --> 39:03.150
♪ Every one of them gives me the strength
not to fear being hurt ♪

39:01.550 --> 39:04.010
I didn't expect those boys
to actually do it.

39:05.030 --> 39:05.630
All thanks to

39:05.630 --> 39:07.480
Your Highness, the dazzling genius.

39:07.480 --> 39:09.610
Of course. I put a lot of effort into it.

39:16.710 --> 39:18.110
Hello, Ms. Lin.

39:18.130 --> 39:19.930
I'm Celeste from Hengjiu Group.

39:20.590 --> 39:22.760
Hengjiu... Do we know each other?

39:23.230 --> 39:24.430
She's looking for me.

39:24.840 --> 39:26.370
Why don't you go back first?

39:30.030 --> 39:31.290
Celeste, of the sky...

39:44.150 --> 39:46.440
She knows my English name means "sky."

39:46.440 --> 39:48.550
Ms. Lin is really a top student.

39:48.570 --> 39:50.300
What does it have to do with you?

39:51.190 --> 39:52.650
Let's talk about Hengjiu.

39:52.710 --> 39:53.640
Not interested.

39:56.110 --> 39:57.640
Why are you walking so fast?

39:57.760 --> 39:59.440
My endurance has always been
better than yours.

39:59.440 --> 40:00.360
I passed when

40:00.360 --> 40:03.230
the sports school recruited me
because I prioritized the big picture.

40:03.230 --> 40:04.630
Weren't you eliminated because

40:04.630 --> 40:05.690
you were too short?

40:06.400 --> 40:07.150
Shut up.

40:08.670 --> 40:11.200
Anyway, if you don't go,
I'll nag you to death.

40:13.710 --> 40:14.800
Want some wontons?

40:15.760 --> 40:16.960
With a lard soup base.

40:20.230 --> 40:22.330
Yes, the one right around the corner.

40:22.480 --> 40:23.070
OK.

40:33.760 --> 40:35.430
You found this place?

40:35.630 --> 40:37.200
It's not your style.

40:37.400 --> 40:38.400
Are you losing it?

40:38.760 --> 40:39.360
Enjoy.

40:39.380 --> 40:40.710
-Thank you.
-Thank you.

40:40.920 --> 40:42.280
Who else is coming?

40:42.280 --> 40:43.410
You'll know in a bit.

40:44.670 --> 40:46.330
Don't eat too much spicy food.

40:46.480 --> 40:47.230
Ms. Wang.

40:49.030 --> 40:49.760
Coach Wang.

40:50.370 --> 40:50.800
Sit.

40:51.420 --> 40:52.000
OK.

40:52.670 --> 40:53.800
Have you ever cared about me?

40:53.800 --> 40:54.960
I can eat by myself.

41:00.070 --> 41:01.200
You've already met.

41:01.670 --> 41:03.230
Mr. Zhang from Hengjiu Youth Football

41:03.230 --> 41:04.690
wants to talk to you again.

41:04.880 --> 41:05.590
Coach Wang,

41:05.590 --> 41:06.920
you rejected me before,

41:07.030 --> 41:08.320
but Ms. Wang thinks

41:08.320 --> 41:10.380
we should keep trying to win you over.

41:10.440 --> 41:11.000
Today,

41:11.000 --> 41:12.800
I brought all our players' info.

41:13.110 --> 41:13.880
I know

41:13.880 --> 41:15.360
you excel at training

41:15.360 --> 41:16.280
star players.

41:17.920 --> 41:20.480
This is the info
on our current team's players.

41:20.480 --> 41:21.280
Look,

41:21.280 --> 41:22.840
there are many stellar players

41:22.840 --> 41:24.770
who can compete internationally.

41:25.030 --> 41:26.320
Hengjiu will be a better place

41:26.320 --> 41:28.180
for you to showcase your talents.

41:28.630 --> 41:29.280
No thanks.

41:30.360 --> 41:31.760
I'm not joining Hengjiu.

41:32.070 --> 41:33.800
And I hope this is the last time

41:33.800 --> 41:35.330
I have to express my stance.

41:35.900 --> 41:37.360
-But Coach Wang...
-Wait.

41:37.840 --> 41:39.900
Do you know my Chinese name is Wang Fa?

41:40.920 --> 41:42.720
Your Ms. Wang is named Wang Tian.

41:44.230 --> 41:45.440
Get it now?

41:48.150 --> 41:49.880
Alright, you can go back.

41:51.760 --> 41:54.210
I'll have a good talk with my brother.

41:54.590 --> 41:55.540
Got it.

42:01.880 --> 42:03.610
Do you have to be so ungrateful?

42:04.550 --> 42:05.590
Hengjiu's football team

42:05.590 --> 42:07.840
is leagues ahead of Hongjing's.

42:09.280 --> 42:10.710
If I wanted a good team,

42:10.710 --> 42:11.630
they'd be lining up for me.

42:11.630 --> 42:13.150
Exactly,

42:13.150 --> 42:15.330
so why must you choose Hongjing?

42:15.710 --> 42:17.840
For the thrill of an underdog victory?

42:19.030 --> 42:19.800
I guess so.

42:20.920 --> 42:23.110
Sis, are your hormones acting up lately

42:23.110 --> 42:24.350
because of your age?

42:25.030 --> 42:26.000
Always worrying about me.

42:26.000 --> 42:27.110
I don't need your concern.

42:27.110 --> 42:27.840
You brat,

42:27.840 --> 42:29.370
what are you talking about?

42:29.800 --> 42:32.550
Worrying about you? Oh, please.

42:33.150 --> 42:35.590
Hengjiu Youth Football is
missing a good coach,

42:35.590 --> 42:36.400
and I also

42:36.400 --> 42:38.800
want to boost the club's revenue
in the next two years.

42:38.800 --> 42:41.470
You're quite cost-effective.

42:41.760 --> 42:45.020
Selling your brother for money?
So it's all business.

42:45.560 --> 42:47.270
Would you let me sell you?

42:47.360 --> 42:49.870
You ruined a perfect win-win.

42:50.760 --> 42:52.220
-Here you are.
-Thank you.

43:01.440 --> 43:03.770
Lin Wanxing brought you here, didn't she?

43:07.070 --> 43:08.030
I get it.

43:08.360 --> 43:10.400
You like Lin Wanxing.

43:10.400 --> 43:11.450
That's why you refuse to leave.

43:11.350 --> 43:12.400
♪ A starlit night ♪

43:11.550 --> 43:12.810
Your wontons are cold.

43:13.240 --> 43:17.690
♪ Secrets falling into my palm ♪

43:13.590 --> 43:14.620
Wang Fa!

43:15.510 --> 43:16.390
You're doomed.

43:17.920 --> 43:18.550
Yes.

43:18.530 --> 43:19.810
♪ Unraveling the mystery ♪

43:19.480 --> 43:20.360
So what?

43:20.570 --> 43:24.600
♪ It was you who gave me this brilliance ♪

43:25.630 --> 43:26.810
♪ Lasting memories ♪

43:27.320 --> 43:32.210
♪ The distance
that brings our dreams closer ♪

43:32.840 --> 43:33.700
♪ To run toward you ♪

43:34.380 --> 43:38.960
♪ I keep practicing with no turning back ♪
